<br>
Blackened salt crystals  are found off the grimling... don't remember exactly which.<br>
White Sand - Bags of this drop off at least the grimling fishermen and mystics<br>
ashes of a grimling shaman shaman dark ritual - drop of grimling mystics<br>
<br>
Molds for the claws are given to the warriors by Khala Dun Kuash (Kuash can be found <br>
at the north gate) for completing two errands.  First being to get 4 &quot;young wolf cub paws&quot; <br>
from sonic wolves.  These are no drop and drop of &quot;sonic wolf pup&quot;, &quot;sonic wolvling&quot;, and <br>
&quot;sonic wolf&quot;.  You have to put the 4 paws into a bag and hit combind.  Once you give the  <br>
bag back to Kuash, he gives you a paper and sends you to the outpost in the grimling forest<br>
to give it to someone.  Sorry I don't remember who you give it to.  She is in the first building on <br>
right as you enter the outpost walls.  (Hard to miss because there are just SO many building in<br>
the outpost ;P)  She is the person on the left as you enter the building.  It's a one room building <br>
with only two people in it so it's easy to find her.  She gives the paper back to you and sends you<br>
to see a guard in hollowshade moor.  He is one of the guards at the fenced in fort just outside the <br>
entrace to hollowshadow more from Shar Val.  He gives the paper back to you and sends you back to <br>
Kuash.  Kuash then gives you TWO molds, a hilt and tells you to go see Qua to get you kit and the<br>
books.  I BELIEVE that the beastlords get a claw and everyone else gets a blade....  But don't <br>
Quote me on that....  <br>
